by thunderingskies

The first time that Jungkook meets Min Yoongi in person, it’s five-thirty in the morning and he’s absolutely soaked to the bone.
So, great first impression.
Thankfully, Yoongi helps show Jungkook that there’s more than meets the eye when it comes to life- and if he falls a little in love along the way? Well, that’s just a bonus.
